All Classes and Interfaces

Class
Description
BankingOffer
Main class, all other classes used in model extends this class.
BestBankingOffer
Class contains program entry point(main), creates controller with args passed to the constructor.
Controller
Controller class, this class controls application logic.
CreditOffer
Subcalss - represent credit offer of the bank (specifies type of the offer by using BankingOffer.setOfferType(java.lang.String) in the constructor).
GraphicalUserInterface
Graphical user interface class, hybrid combination of controller and pure view class generated by NetBeans GUIBuilder, and modified.
GuiTextContent
Graphical user interface text content class, this class store text that is always displayed.
PersonalAccountOffer
Subcalss - represent personal account offer of the bank (specifies type of the offer by using BankingOffer.setOfferType(java.lang.String) in the constructor).
TextUserInterface
Text user interface class, this class is used for program interaction with console.
TypeException
User exception class - extends RuntimeException.
